        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3121424880" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8688635872161129341">A wonderful ghost story!<br/><br/>The Canterville Ghost is a delightful gentle horror story. The story&apos;s set in Canterville Chase, which for many centuries has been haunted by the ghost of Sir Simon. An American minister and his family moves in, and it is no longer normal for the &quot;resident&quot; ghost. The story is also about how an act of kindness can help even ghosts find peace.<br/><br/>This one&apos;s a fun read.</span>
  <span id="freeText8688635872161129341" style="display:none">A wonderful ghost story!<br /><br />The Canterville Ghost is a delightful gentle horror story. The story's set in Canterville Chase, which for many centuries has been haunted by the ghost of Sir Simon. An American minister and his family moves in, and it is no longer normal for the "resident" ghost. The story is also about how an act of kindness can help even ghosts find peace.<br /><br />This one's a fun read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8688635872161129341" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
