  <span id="freeText14560949817410448653" style="display:none"><b>actual rating: 4.5 stars</b><br /><br />Not this being the funniest gothic novel I've read!! Americans hazing and taunting a GHOST, SCARIng him and making him feel insecure about his spooky ways eye- <br /><br />This was insanely fun and quick too!! And then there's a definite change in the narrative; it becomes a lot more somber as the ghost starts to think about death, loneliness &amp; the power of love. </span>
